Return the percent of complete values

####  Description 

The complement to ``pct_miss``

####  Usage 
<pre><code>
pct_complete(x)
</code></pre>

#### Arguments 

* ``x``: vector or data.frame

#### Examples 
```{r}
pct_complete(airquality)
pct_complete(airquality$Ozone)
```

#### Value 

numeric percent of complete values
